# Credential Status List

The credential status list API lets you issue and revoke credentials, and request the status list. Credential issuers can use this API to validate their own credentials.

In this section you can find information about:

* [issuing a status list entry](issue-status-list-entry/)
* [revoking a credential](revoke-credential/)
* [getting a status list](statuslist/)